[{"ave_id":"AVE-2001-0001","file_name":"2001/AVE-2001-0001.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2001-0537","title":"Cisco IOS HTTP配置任意管理访问漏洞","description":"思科 IOS 11.x/12.x 版本的 HTTP 配置接口存在认证绕过漏洞。攻击者可通过向目标设备的 HTTP 配置服务发送特制请求，无需有效凭据即可获取管理员级别的访问权限，完全控制目标路由器或交换机。该漏洞影响广泛部署的 Cisco IOS 11.x 及 12.x 系列版本，攻击者可借此篡改网络配置、窃取流量或发动进一步攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-2001-0537"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2001-07-21","updated":"2001-07-21","remediation":"升级 Cisco IOS 至 12.1(5)T 及之后或 12.2(1) 及之后已修复版本。如无需 HTTP 管理功能，通过全局配置命令 `no ip http server` 禁用 HTTP 服务；若需保留 Web 管理，配置 `ip http authentication aaa` 启用 AAA 认证并设置 `ip http access-class` 限制可访问的源 IP 范围，同时建议改用 HTTPS（配置 `ip http secure-server`）替代明文 HTTP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20978","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2001/CVE-2001-0537.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2001/CVE-2001-0537.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/a5c2e8e4dab8c8e618ba76807c3e07587b7d781a/http/cves/2001/CVE-2001-0537.yaml","https://github.com/PortSwigger/BChecks/blob/7117c5ff8d1d47ca6282020a243b4d3026480ad5/vulnerabilities-CVEd/CVE-2001-0537%20CISCO%20Authentication%20Bypass.bcheck","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d5838f491a2d04e9f823fb9638e9e6f0b038d399/cves/2001/0xxx/CVE-2001-0537.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2001-0537_5_1.yaml","https://github.com/e-m-b-a/emba/blob/968abdc74763b43a3cdd216fbb1950cab484f982/config/msf_cve-db.txt","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2001-0537_3.yaml","https://github.com/daxtar2/Guts/blob/885dac464c9948f7809c239b00901699cd593827/templates/http/cves/2001/CVE-2001-0537.yaml","https://github.com/NCNU-OpenSource/Web-Vulnerability/blob/f1cebd5bb195876b1f60997368ee1be28fdb89a7/README.md","https://github.com/TonyStark1109/JARVIS-MARK-5/blob/756e6a7362ebce8a56e07f16413733ad23d90c7a/nuclei-templates/http/cves/2001/CVE-2001-0537.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2001/AVE-2001-0001.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2001-0002","file_name":"2001/AVE-2001-0002.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2001-1473","title":"SSH SSH-1协议私钥计算漏洞","description":"SSH-1 协议在会话密钥协商过程中存在设计缺陷，远程攻击者可通过中间人攻击方式伪造与目标服务器相同的 Session ID，同时使用弱公钥对替换合法公钥，从而计算出对应的私钥。攻击者利用已破解的密钥对即可劫持会话并伪装成目标服务器，实现对加密通信的窃听与篡改。该漏洞影响所有使用 SSH-1 协议的系统与客户端，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。建议升级至 SSH-2 协议以彻底规避此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2001-1473"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2001-01-18T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:56:20.683","remediation":"禁用 SSH-1 协议，仅使用 SSH-2。检查服务器 OpenSSH 配置（/etc/ssh/sshd_config），将 Protocol 设置为 2，并重启 sshd 服务。客户端也需禁用 SSH-1 兼容模式（Protocol 2）。对于老旧系统无法升级 OpenSSH 的，建议升级到支持 SSH-2 的版本（如 OpenSSH 3.4p1 及以上）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.kb.cert.org/vuls/id/684820","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/6603","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/network/cves/2001/CVE-2001-1473.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2001/CVE-2001-1473.md","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/CVE-2001-1473.yaml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d5838f491a2d04e9f823fb9638e9e6f0b038d399/cves/2001/1xxx/CVE-2001-1473.json","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2001/CVE-2001-1473.rules","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2001-1473_1.yaml","https://github.com/veo/vscan/blob/1beb10c08e377e15b7dd417be1843bb75aa8c4f0/pocs_yml/nucleiFiles/cves/2001/CVE-2001-1473.yaml","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2001-1473_4.yaml","https://github.com/itsmenaga/Nuclei-Templates-All/blob/7e93c24e44969db15f4072e1c6a322a026452d6b/Vulnerability-Templates/cve-2001-1473-1299.yaml","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-debian/blob/b504c563e52b82e368fb82bf2033317b7c351e61/tracker/CVE/2001/CVE-2001-1473.json","https://github.com/linuxadi/40k-nuclei-templates/blob/542be6820c801c02a33aee60f1c05ca7b0b5005f/aditya/folder5/cve-2001-1473-1300.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2001/AVE-2001-0002.toml"}]